{"/service/ndnp/kyu/batch_kyu_heeler_ver01/data/sn86069242/00516998180/1920121601/0522.xml":{"full_text":"Thursday December 16\nTHE ANDERSON NEWS\nv\nThe Stuart Shop\n-V\nWithjtfce best line of GIFTS ever offered -Prices\na tittle under anywhere\nelse Exclusive\u2014\nDOLLS BAGS NOVELTIES\nV\nfc\nHandkerchiefs from 16c to $250\nChristmas Cards for Everybody\nThose Wonderful Boxed Bulbs!\nOpposite\nPostoffice\nFrankfort Ky\nDEMOCRAT FLOOR LEADER\nIN LAST LEGISLATURE\nOPPOSES EXTRA SESSION\nWonderful Variety Beauty\nand Values\nCHRISTMAS\nPRESENTS\nOur Holiday stocks in all lines are larger than usual this\nyear We have been able to secure fine quality goods and\nplenty of them at reasonable prices The result is a mag\nnificent showing of the very choicest kind of Christmas pres\nents for men women boys girls and babies at prices that\nmean genuine economy to you\nIVORY CELLULOID\nThe newest ideas in colored and white patterns Sets and\nSingle Pieces\n$1350 to $8500\nSILVERWARE\nInnumerable fine gifts in hollow ware just the thing for\nthe home lover All pieces of flatware in beautiful pat\nterns Chests of Silver\n$1350 to $50000\nJEWELRY\nExquisite jeweled and engraved articles A treasure house\nof presents\nParis Ky Dec 2 1920\nHon B L Cox\nLawrenceburg Ky\nDear Sir:\u2014\nI received a message from\nthe Courier-Journal asking for\nmy views on the question of an\nextra session of the Legislature\npresume a like inquiry was\nmade of other members I re\nplied as follows:\n'Considering the condition\nof business generally I think it\nwould be unwise to hold a spe\ncial session of the Legislature at\nhis time The people are al\nready suffering from business\ndepression as well as tax bur\ndens To increase these un\nnecessarily would be a great in'\njustice to the tax payers\n\u2018We were taught during the\nstress of the war to concen\ntrate our efforts to the produc\ntion of necessities also to elim\ninate all but the most urgent\nwork Public improvements\nwere practically abandoned\nduring that period Business\nconditions are moreunsettled\nnow than at that time and no\none can foretell when they\nwill change for the better Con\nditions at present demand the\nstrictest economy as well as the\nmost judicious expendiures o:\npublic funds Money appropri\nated for any purpose will be di\nverted from business chan\nnets\u201d\nIf the Republicans are seek\ning an extra session it is for\nother purposes than those men\ntioned by the advocates of\nspecial road fund The annullec\nwhiskey tax was not regarde\nseriously as a revenue produc\ner The other measures tha\nare now' being suggested were\nrejected by the last Legislature\nI see no occasion for repeating\nthat performance at the ex\npense of the taxpayers\nSince the Republicans have\nbeen repudiated in the recent\nState election it is not unrea\nsonable to suspect that they are\npreparing to intrench them\nselves against a Democratic\nLegislature which will be elect\ned next Fall under present ap\npointment It is reported tha\nOther matters will be included\nby the Governor in the call for\nan extra session\nI think under the circum\nstances the Democratic mem\nbers should be careful not to\ncommit themselves to any prop\nosition whatever holding them\nselves free to- act on all ques\ntions as they are presentee\nPersonally I shall take no ac\ntion which might injure the\nDemocratic cause in the future\nWith kindest regards I am\nVery truly yours\nJAS H THOMPSON\nFancy Stone Rings\nCameos\nMen's Rings\nBar Pins\nPendants\nSmall Pins\nCuff Links -Watch\nChains\nLockets for Babies\n\u2019Extra good values in fine high-grade unmounted Diamonds\nand Gold and Platinum Diamond Jewelry\nWATCHES\nA large stock for men and women\njFor men $250 to $15000\nBracelet Watches $1500 to $5001)0\nOTHER GOOD SUGGESTIONS\nFountain jFens Military Brushes Smoking Stands CigaN\ncite Cases Vanities Mesh Bags Toiletware Manicure\nPieces Clacks Cut Glass\nm a selbert\nESTABLISHED IN 1872\nJEWELER\n330 ST C